<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" size="6">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="4"><i>Chartered By The British Schools Foundation</i></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#c0c0c0" size="6"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: right;"><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><br></span></font></div><div><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><div><div><div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">The health and safety of your children is our top priority. In addition to taking all necessary&nbsp;precautions, we aim to always keep our parents well informed of anything which comes to our&nbsp;attention which may affect your children.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">I am writing to inform you that there has been a confirmed case of chickenpox, and influenza&nbsp;in two pupils in our&nbsp;Year 1 classes.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Chickenpox is a contagious and mild virus which is extremely common amongst young&nbsp;children. It causes a rash of red, itchy spots that turn into blisters and eventually fall off. Symptoms&nbsp;usually go away without treatment, but because the infection is very contagious, an infected child&nbsp;should stay home and rest until the symptoms are gone.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">If your child exhibits symptoms, please keep&nbsp;them away from school, let us know and seek appropriate medical attention.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">For further information about chickenpox please <a href="http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/chickenpox/Pages/Introduction.aspx">follow this link</a></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></div></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Influenza is an infectious illness that is caused by a virus which affects the respiratory&nbsp;system – nose, throat and lungs. It is spread by droplets from someone who is coughing or through&nbsp;contact. Small children are very susceptible as they touch everything and are constantly putting their&nbsp;hands onto their face and into their mouth.&nbsp;Symptoms include: fever, body aches, chills, dizziness,&nbsp;headaches, nausea, vomiting, sore throat, runny nose and fatigue. Please seek immediate medical&nbsp;advice and advise the school promptly if your child is unwell with any of the above symptoms.</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><div><br></div><div>At school, we are taking all precautions necessary including:&nbsp;</div><div><ul><li>Implementing good hygiene measures</li><li>Daily cleaning and disinfection of surfaces, door handles, stair railings, toys, bathroom accessories and food utensils</li><li>Early Years’ toys thoroughly disinfected every Friday</li><li>Unwell children will see nurse and if necessary parents will be contacted</li><li>The children have been taught how to wash their hands by teachers and also how to cover their mouths and noses when coughing or sneezing</li></ul></div><div>If you believe your child has influenza, please seek medical treatment, follow safety procedures at home and keep them away from school until they have recovered from the illness.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>For further information about influenza, please <a href="
http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/Flu/Pages/Introduction.aspx">follow this link</a></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><br></div></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span id="docs-internal-guid-739f9671-aa49-80e0-901b-21c29fb501ed"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><p dir="ltr" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Best regards</span></p><font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Alison Mackey</font></font></span></div></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><font size="4" face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Deputy Head of Primary</b></font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><br></div></span></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; text-align: center;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font><font class="